msgstr "生成该二进制文件时使用了哪个版本的 Mandrel？"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "One can see which Mandrel version was used to generate a binary by inspecting the binary as follows:"
msgstr "可以通过以下方式检查二进制文件，从而了解生成该二进制文件时使用的 Mandrel 版本："

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.16/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "How do I enable GC logging in native executables?"
msgstr "如何在原生可执行文件中启用垃圾回收日志记录？"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See <<gc-logging,Native Memory Management GC Logging section>> for details."
msgstr "详情请参阅 xref:gc-logging[“本机内存管理 GC 日志记录”一节] 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.16/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Can I get a heap dump of a native executable? e.g. if it runs out of memory"
msgstr "能否获取原生可执行文件的堆转储？例如，当它内存不足时"

#. type: Plain text
